      "span_text": "Such a computation has in fact never been performed at LO. This allows us to question the size of the DPS yield assumed by ATLAS based on their W + 2-jet analysis  and to propose a solution for the present puzzle with a DPS yield roughly three times larger (yet compatible with the 1-σ upper value set by ATLAS)."
